{"title":"难忘山道","authors":["黄桢国"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘山道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄桢国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从葳蕤中走出纯朴的魂灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载着贫瘠的山坳让人记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我的母亲、我的妹妹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用披星戴月的艰辛送我启程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此心总沉甸甸负载这山道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一条很深很深的烙印没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有高智商的时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛再好奇也望不到山外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"课堂里我补裰祖辈的向往"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡的山道导引我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跋—涉—远—方"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}